des:
Passing the Parcel Game is a fantastic game for kids and adults.
The hilarious tasks assigned to those who lose will keep everyone entertained. 

Game plays music, has interesting quotes, and give unique tasks for the ones who get out. 

The perfect party game for get-together and other occasions.
